    <div class="heading-and-paragraph__wrapper maxwidth">
        <h1 class="h1-medium heading-and-paragraph__heading">
            About Us        </h1>
        <p class="heading-and-paragraph__paragraph">
            Alter Engineers was founded by passionate engineers who have a history of collaboration in HVAC and plumbing design for High Performance and Zero Net Energy and water building designs. The company was created out of the desire to make the team's vast experience in low energy, all-electric, and water building systems attainable to a wider audience with a focus on the greater San Francisco Bay Area.        </p>
